Package code

This package contains all model classes of the code representation.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CodeParent
    Interface implemented by the classes of the model to reference a parent class, provides a method the get its name
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CodeClass
    Class representing a class, extending CodeElement
    CodeConstructor
    Represents a constructor of a CodeElement
    CodeElement
    Abstract class extended by CodeClasses, CodeInterfaces and CodeEnumerations
    CodeEnumeration
    Class representing an enumeration, extending CodeElement, has a additional list of CodeLiterals
    CodeField
    Represents a field of a CodeElement
    CodeInterface
    Class representing an interface, extending CodeElement
    CodeLiteral
    Represents a literal of a CodeEnumeration
    CodeMethod
    Represents a method of a CodeElement
    CodeModifier
    Class providing a static method to convert the modifiers of a CodeElement, CodeField, CodeMethod or a CodeParameter to an integer value to use the methods inherited by Modifier.
    CodeModifierTest
    Test class testing the CodeModifier.convertModifierValue(code.CodeVisibility, boolean, boolean, boolean)
    CodePackage
    A package containing CodeElements and other sub-CodePackages
    CodeParameter
    Represents a parameter of a CodeMethod
    CodeRepresentation
    Root element of the code representation, has a list of CodePackages which contain all of the elements.
    CodeTemplateBinding
    Represents a template binding of a CodeElement or CodeMethod
    CodeTemplateParameter
    Represents a template parameter of a CodeElement or CodeMethod
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CodeVisibility
    Enumeration containing literals representing access modifiers.

Package code Description

This package contains all model classes of the code representation.
